====Verb====
{{en-verb}}

# To keep a [[vehicle]] pointed in a certain [[direction]].
# To guide by means of a device such as a [[rudder]], [[paddle]], or [[wheel]].
# To [[direct]] a [[group]] of [[animal]]s.
# To [[direct]] the [[conversation]], or [[influence]] a point of view.
# To [[maneuver]] or [[manipulate]] a [[person]] or [[group]] into a [[place]] or [[course]] of [[action]].

